 <purpose>
   <p>
     This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the
     representation of task elements and their ordering constructs.
   </p>
 </purpose>

 <!-- Items in scope -->
 <inscope>
   <li>Task step - the basic idea of some element in an ordered sequence of tasks;</li>
   <li>Task loop controls;</li>
   <li>Task sequence;</li>
   <li>Task branches;</li>
   <li>Task end points;</li>
   <li>Task relationships and task assignment.</li>
 </inscope>

 <!-- Items out of scope -->
